---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-dark-50 mb-6">About TechVerse</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>
        TechVerse is an AI-powered knowledge hub dedicated to exploring the most fascinating frontiers
        of science and technology. From the quantum realm to the vast cosmos, from cutting-edge algorithms
        to the wonders of the natural world — we cover it all.
      </p>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>
        Every article on TechVerse is generated through an innovative AI-powered pipeline:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Topic Selection</strong> — A new topic is submitted via GitHub Issues</li>
        <li><strong>AI Generation</strong> — Google Gemini 2.0 Flash researches and writes a comprehensive article</li>
        <li><strong>Auto Publishing</strong> — The article is automatically committed, built, and deployed</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Topics We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Computer Science</strong> — Algorithms, data structures, programming paradigms, and software engineering</li>
        <li><strong>Space Technology</strong> — Rockets, satellites, space exploration, and astrophysics</li>
        <li><strong>Artificial Intelligence</strong> — Machine learning, neural networks, LLMs, and robotics</li>
        <li><strong>Quantum Physics</strong> — Quantum computing, entanglement, superposition, and quantum mechanics</li>
        <li><strong>Nature</strong> — Ecology, biology, climate science, and the wonders of the natural world</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Open Source</h2>
      <p>
        TechVerse is fully open source. The entire site, including the AI content generation pipeline,
        is available on GitHub. Feel free to fork it and create your own AI-powered blog!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
